race.comment: FLYING ANIMO (4) resumes here but the form he has displayed in previous campaigns was good enough for a race of this nature. Looks the runner in this field with the most upside and should prove tough to hold out. DISCOVERED GOLD (2) goes well for hoop Silvera Olivera who is yet to miss a place in five rides. Racing consistently of late and is sure to run well again. MOMENT OF TRUTH (6) has never missed a drum in six starts around this circuit and gets some weight off from the low draw. Ticks a few boxes. NOBLE INTENT (8) has been thereabouts in recent outings and may earn some minor money. OFFICE POLITICS (9) is a last-start winner who shouldn't be slept on.
